data.description: Amazing opportunity to live in the desired Virginia Beach neighborhood of Pembroke Meadows. Near to Town Center, this home is near a multitude of restaurants and as Town Center continues to grow, so will the entertainment options! This home boasts a private inground pool and the neighborhood also has a public pool that can be accessed with an optional annual fee. Situated just before a cul de sac, this street has very light traffic. If you are looking to move to Virginia Beach, you don't want to miss out on this one! 2 Cats in the home. Please do not let them out. They are indoor cats. Ring camera on premises.
